Running smoothly at Cyberport.

Looking for a 10km run in Hong Kong? Coach @rob_the_global_kiwi has mapped out the perfect coastal route at Cyberport 🌊. Perfect for urban runners who like to challenge themselves, the panoramic views will make every step worthwhile!

Lace up your Clifton 10, engineered for everyday runs, and feel how they transform Cyberport’s challenging inclines into a smoother, lighter, and more stable stride!

Stay tuned for more 10km route inspirations, and let’s discover more Hong Kong‘s hidden gems on foot in the smoothest ride ever!

🔗 Ready to elevate your 10K runs? Tap the link in bio and explore our HOKA Clifton 10k route recommendation now!

想尋找香港10公里跑步路線？今次 Coach Rob @rob_the_global_kiwi 為你介紹一條沿海而跑的路線🌊－數碼港，適合希望挑戰自己的跑者，沿途景色絕對令你一跑難忘！

立即穿上專為日常跑步而設的 Clifton 10，即使面對數碼港這條比較多斜路的路線，也可享受更流暢、更輕量及更穩定的跑步體驗！

想以跑步探索香港不同角落？記得密切留意 @hoka_hongkong ，我們將會為你分享更多10公里路線！一起Run Smooth，跑得更無拘無束🏃🏃‍♀️！
